At key moments, we store full snapshots:

---

## SNAPSHOT STRUCTURE

```json id="in5"
{
  "timestamp": 123456,
  "nodeId": "puzzle_001",
  "state": {
    "inventory": {},
    "flags": {},
    "stats": {}
  }
}
```

---

## WHEN TO SNAPSHOT

* node enter
* node exit
* after effects batch
* before transition execution

